1) Ibice byose bihuye nibikoresho bikozwe mubyuma 316 bidafite ingese;igice cyikaramu gikozwe mubyuma 304 bidafite ingese, nta bicuruzwa byuma, nibicuruzwa byujuje ubuziranenge bwa GMP.
2) Ibigize pneumatike nibicuruzwa byamashanyarazi nibicuruzwa bizwi cyane byo muri Tayiwani AIRTAC, Mitsubishi yo mu Buyapani na Schneider;
3) Nozzle yuzuza ifite anti-drip kandi ikora uburyo bwo kuzuza ubwoko;
4) Menya muri rusange ihinduka ryihuse ryuzuye ryuzuye, ryerekanwa na compteur;ingano yuzuye ya buri mutwe irashobora kuba kugiti cye neza, byoroshye kandi byihuse.Imashini ifite ibikorwa byogusukura byikora.
5) Ukoresheje gahunda yo kugenzura porogaramu ya PLC, gukoraho-ubwoko bwimashini-imashini, gushiraho ibipimo biroroshye kandi byihuse.
6) Igice cyuzuye cyuzuza igice cyihuta, cyoroshye mugusukura no gusenya

Ikoreshwa
Ibicuruzwa birakwiriye ibyuma (bateri ya alkaline, bateri ya buto, kole), ububiko (ikaramu ikaramu, gusiba, amazi yo gukosora, kole ikomeye), umukino wa moto na moto (feri, feri), ibikenerwa bya buri munsi (urwembe, koza amenyo, icyuma gifata ), kwisiga (lipstick, gukuramo imisumari, parufe) nibindi bicuruzwa bijyanye ninganda bipfunyika amakarita.
Imikorere
(1).Imashini ya CAM, kugenzura moteri ya servo, imikorere yoroshye;
(2).Umubiri wibyuma, isura nziza, isuku yoroshye;
.
